Revision history for Mojolicious-Plugin-PstemplateRenderer

0.01 2011/03/23
  - initial release

0.02 2011/03/31
  - some natie helpers available

0.03 2011/04/22
  - Improved error logging

0.04 2011/05/16
  - ActionBase class added for frameworking

0.05 2011/05/17
  - Template not found now causes die

0.06 2011/05/18
  - API got simple

0.07 2011/05/18
  - ComponentBase got some utility functions for template

0.08 2011/05/19
  - Controller no longer given via second arg on tpl funcs

0.09 2011/05/19
  - Distribution renamed

0.10 2011/05/20
  - Mojo::Tusu::plug for hooking MojoX::Tusu::ComponentBase::init

0.11 2011/05/23
  - Template dir and static dir both now defaults to public_html

0.12 2011/05/26
  - Exception object explicitly stringified

0.13 2011/05/31
  - Extensions_to_render method added

0.14 2011/06/01
  - document_root method optimized & bug fixed

0.15 2011/06/01
  - plug method now capable of multiple plugins at once

0.16 2011/06/01
  - Reduce messing app attr namaspace

0.17 2011/06/08
  - File searching rule has been changed. It got similar behavior to apache 
  - directory_index method added
  - Compatibility with apache improved
  - bootstrap renewed

0.18 2011/06/10
  - url_abs added
  - Permission check activated
  - Directory Index can be a static file now
  - Fixed a bug on CGI mode
  - pst handler removed and tusu is available
  - error document method added
  
0.19 2011/06/20

  - Pathes in templates without trailing slash are no longer autofilled with
    directory index
  - FIX: CGI mode bug on root access
  - input & output encoding can be auto detected
  
0.20 2011/06/21
  - Mojolicious::Command::Generate::TusuApp added
  - Static file bug on win fixed

0.21 2011/06/22
  - ini and ini_set added in ComponentBase
  - Depencency updated

0.22 2011/06/30
  - output_encoding feature no longer available. Consider using
    Plack::Middleware instead.
  - Permission check is eased to inside document root

0.23 2011/06/30
